Package dungeonette.generator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Architect
    Architect contains the main loop used for generating the dungeon floors.
    DoorInserter
    This class places doorways into the dungeon after the passages have been carved.
    DungeonPrinter
    Prints out the finished dunngeon, floor by floor
    PassageCarver
    Class used to generate passages between existing rooms.
    RoomDecorator
    Class used to decorate newly constructed rooms with random items, furniture and such.
    RoomInserter
    Class used to examine wether a room of specific size can be placed on a specific location of a floor
    RoomShaper
    This class gives the basic rectangular shape to a room.
    RoomStrangifier
    This class gives an alternative shape for a room.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Architect.Dir
    This enum represents north, south, east and west .
